metadata.description:
SPOTLIGHT WK 7

Following SATELLITES, we dropped a free sample pack with Kits.io and urged the community to hit us with their best remixes/beats. Sara Phillips' submission was one that instantly swept us off our feet. The tender vocals take front and center in this track, supported by bits and pieces of production off the Satellites project. 

Here's some words of wisdom from the artist herself:
